Package algorithm

Class Sudoku

java.lang.Object
algorithm.Sudoku
public class Sudoku extends Object
Main class for setting up the exact cover problem with the constraints for Sudoku. This class will call the Dancing Links algorithm X runner, DLX.java.
Author:
Robert Wilson Created: 09 DEC S2022 Class: CS 5800

  • Method Details

    • solve

      public boolean solve()
      Converts the Sudoku problem into an Exact cover problem with the proper constraints. Then it creates a quadruple chained list and calls the DLX solve method, Algorithm X. Lastly it converts the solution back to a human readable sudoku solution. If there is a solution it returns true and if not then it returns false.
      Returns:
      solved (boolean) true if it has a solution and false otherwise.
